TRYPANOSOMIASIS - BRAZIL: REQUEST FOR INFO
******************************************
ProMED-mail post
[see: Salivarian trypanosomes, meeting on the Internet 96xxxxxx]
Date: Tue, 3 Mar 1998 09:37:04 -0600
From: Dr. Cristobal Zepeda <czepeda@ns1.oirsa.org.sv

Lately I have heard of an outbreak of what seems to be trypanosomiasis in
Brasil. However I have not seen an official report. Can someone give more
information on this?
